1
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:23,900
"Journey With You"

2
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:26,700
(Episode 7)

3
00:01:51,911 --> 00:01:53,871
It's said that Jiangnan
produces beautiful women.

4
00:01:54,113 --> 00:01:55,113
In my opinion,

5
00:01:55,548 --> 00:01:57,717
although these beauties
all have some charm,

6
00:01:58,151 --> 00:01:59,752
compared with Concubine Chen,

7
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:01,988
they all pale in comparison.

8
00:02:02,522 --> 00:02:03,990
If Concubine Chen were still here,

9
00:02:04,090 --> 00:02:07,794
the harem would surely
be much more splendid.

10
00:02:10,830 --> 00:02:12,910
Your Majesty hasn't been
to Jiangnan for many years.

11
00:02:13,299 --> 00:02:15,668
Visiting this place again
after Concubine Chen's passing,

12
00:02:16,069 --> 00:02:18,271
it's inevitable to be reminded of her.

13
00:02:18,771 --> 00:02:20,039
In my opinion,

14
00:02:21,007 --> 00:02:23,643
even Concubine Chen's
spirit in heaven wouldn't want

15
00:02:23,676 --> 00:02:26,713
to see Your Majesty so grieved for her.

16
00:02:28,248 --> 00:02:29,849
The Empress is absolutely right.

17
00:02:30,350 --> 00:02:36,556
After all, Concubine Chen left me
Qi'er and Heshu, such wonderful children.

18
00:02:37,056 --> 00:02:39,726
Now Qi'er has grown up a lot.

19
00:02:39,926 --> 00:02:42,195
It's time for him to stand on his own.

20
00:02:42,962 --> 00:02:43,962
Father,

21
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:45,598
I have another request to make.

22
00:02:46,633 --> 00:02:47,467
Yanzhi used to

23
00:02:47,468 --> 00:02:49,402
serve in Mother's Yonghe Palace.

24
00:02:50,069 --> 00:02:51,571
Mother took him in.

25
00:02:51,971 --> 00:02:53,439
Now that Mother is gone,

26
00:02:54,073 --> 00:02:55,507
I'd like to relieve him

27
00:02:55,508 --> 00:02:57,277
of his duty to guard the imperial city

28
00:02:57,443 --> 00:02:59,045
and give him an idle position.

29
00:02:59,679 --> 00:03:03,216
You've always had a good relationship
with that hostage.

30
00:03:03,483 --> 00:03:05,885
Why do you want to
relieve him of his duties now?

31
00:03:08,321 --> 00:03:09,756
The royal brother is joking.

32
00:03:10,757 --> 00:03:11,791
I think.

33
00:03:12,458 --> 00:03:14,698
Pei Yanzhi is, after all, a
hostage from a foreign land.

34
00:03:14,761 --> 00:03:17,161
We still need to distinguish
between closeness and distance.

35
00:03:18,164 --> 00:03:20,033
I'm very pleased that
Qi'er has such thoughts.

36
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:22,035
I'm truly gratified.

37
00:03:23,736 --> 00:03:24,537
Zhou'er,

38
00:03:24,637 --> 00:03:27,040
don't make fun of your younger brother.

39
00:03:27,974 --> 00:03:28,708
Father,

40
00:03:28,709 --> 00:03:30,509
I was just joking around.

41
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:31,510
Don't take it seriously.

42
00:03:38,251 --> 00:03:39,251
Your Majesty has

43
00:03:39,252 --> 00:03:41,521
been showing great favor
to Qi'er and Heshu lately.

44
00:03:42,755 --> 00:03:44,457
If Concubine Chen were to see this,

45
00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:46,330
she would surely be
overwhelmed with surprise.

46
00:03:48,294 --> 00:03:49,095
Alright,

47
00:03:49,096 --> 00:03:50,416
let's not talk about her anymore.

48
00:03:50,763 --> 00:03:51,763
Empress,

49
00:03:51,798 --> 00:03:53,599
you're also my confidante.

50
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:54,700
Over the years,

51
00:03:54,934 --> 00:03:57,437
you've worked hard managing the harem.

52
00:03:57,937 --> 00:03:59,539
I've beared witness to it all.

53
00:04:00,673 --> 00:04:01,908
Thank you, Your Majesty.

54
00:04:02,108 --> 00:04:03,208
I've just

55
00:04:03,209 --> 00:04:04,977
done what I should do.

56
00:04:06,012 --> 00:04:09,816
I've noticed lately that Zhou'er has
been busy with government affairs

57
00:04:10,049 --> 00:04:11,617
and has lost a lot of weight.

58
00:04:12,285 --> 00:04:13,285
Your Majesty,

59
00:04:13,309 --> 00:04:17,213
why not assign some of the
government affairs to Qi'er?

60
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,935
Father, drink slowly.

61
00:04:31,077 --> 00:04:32,577
I asked the landlady of Yanbo Tower

62
00:04:32,601 --> 00:04:34,169
to prepare some Jinlingchun for you.

63
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,641
I'll go fetch it.

64
00:04:36,976 --> 00:04:39,312
Heshu understands me the best.

65
00:04:40,046 --> 00:04:41,247
Go quickly, go quickly.

66
00:04:45,685 --> 00:04:46,285
Father,

67
00:04:46,286 --> 00:04:47,652
don't be fooled by Heshu.

68
00:04:47,653 --> 00:04:48,321
I think she

69
00:04:48,322 --> 00:04:49,442
just wants to drink herself.

70
00:04:56,195 --> 00:04:57,363
Why are you here?

71
00:04:58,931 --> 00:05:00,199
Why can't I come?

72
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,410
There's no place in Jiangnan City

73
00:05:01,434 --> 00:05:03,403
that this young lady can't go to.

74
00:05:04,003 --> 00:05:05,683
Tell your royal brother and Brother Yanzhi

75
00:05:05,872 --> 00:05:07,607
that we've prepared a great gift for them.

76
00:05:07,707 --> 00:05:09,107
After your family banquet is over,

77
00:05:09,108 --> 00:05:10,510
come with me to see it.

78
00:05:10,843 --> 00:05:11,644
What gift?

79
00:05:11,645 --> 00:05:12,712
Can you tell me now?

80
00:05:12,736 --> 00:05:13,803
Of course not.

81
00:05:14,147 --> 00:05:16,416
Anyway, it's a big catch.

82
00:05:17,917 --> 00:05:18,851
So mysterious.

83
00:05:18,885 --> 00:05:20,353
This princess doesn't even care.

84
00:05:20,987 --> 00:05:22,067
You're just being stubborn.

85
00:05:26,726 --> 00:05:28,761
Qi'er can help relieve my worries,

86
00:05:29,162 --> 00:05:31,230
and Heshu can please me.

87
00:05:31,697 --> 00:05:34,567
This trip to Jiangnan
has been truly enjoyable.

88
00:05:37,236 --> 00:05:38,971
Father is really praising me too highly.

89
00:05:39,204 --> 00:05:40,838
Compared with my royal brother,

90
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,240
I still have a long way to go.

91
00:05:44,877 --> 00:05:46,379
Aunt Lin asked me to tell you

92
00:05:46,412 --> 00:05:47,847
that she's prepared a great gift

93
00:05:48,047 --> 00:05:49,127
for you and Brother Yanzhi.

94
00:05:50,483 --> 00:05:52,351
But she didn't tell me what it is.

95
00:05:53,286 --> 00:05:54,286
Royal brother,

96
00:05:54,353 --> 00:05:55,353
In my opinion,

97
00:05:55,521 --> 00:05:57,190
Father trusts you very much now.

98
00:05:57,490 --> 00:06:02,328
Why not just tell Father about Yin Zhou's
planned rebellion and let him deal with it?

99
00:06:02,895 --> 00:06:04,335
There's no evidence for this matter.

100
00:06:04,397 --> 00:06:05,798
If we say it rashly,

101
00:06:06,532 --> 00:06:08,733
Father will definitely
think I'm deliberately

102
00:06:08,734 --> 00:06:10,694
sowing discord between
him and the royal brother.

103
00:06:11,838 --> 00:06:12,838
That makes sense.

104
00:06:20,379 --> 00:06:21,848
Fifth brother is being too modest.

105
00:06:22,248 --> 00:06:23,649
On this trip to Jiangnan,

106
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:26,018
I've heard several times

107
00:06:27,453 --> 00:06:29,589
from the accompanying officials say that...

108
00:06:32,758 --> 00:06:33,960
What did they say?

109
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,935
I heard them say

110
00:06:36,362 --> 00:06:38,774
that fifth brother has the same demeanor
as Father did in his youth,

111
00:06:38,798 --> 00:06:41,000
resembling Father when he was young.

112
00:06:41,634 --> 00:06:42,968
I've heard that

113
00:06:42,969 --> 00:06:45,449
fifth brother has been getting close
to many ministers lately.

114
00:06:45,638 --> 00:06:48,207
You must have learned a lot, right?

115
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:51,410
They really said that?

116
00:06:53,613 --> 00:06:55,613
Father's heroic bearing
is naturally unparalleled.

117
00:06:56,349 --> 00:06:58,350
I think those officials just said

118
00:06:58,351 --> 00:06:59,952
some flattering words

119
00:07:00,419 --> 00:07:01,897
which, when reaching the
royal elder brother's ears,

120
00:07:01,921 --> 00:07:03,001
have changed their meaning.

121
00:07:03,025 --> 00:07:04,025
Fifth brother,

122
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:06,558
I've also heard that you and that

123
00:07:06,559 --> 00:07:08,227
hostage have an ambiguous relationship.

124
00:07:08,595 --> 00:07:11,130
And now you've relieved him of his duties.

125
00:07:12,485 --> 00:07:14,796
Are you really able to distinguish
between closeness and distance,

126
00:07:15,067 --> 00:07:17,169
or are you afraid that people will find out

127
00:07:17,336 --> 00:07:19,338
that you're colluding with him?

128
00:07:19,485 --> 00:07:20,886
Royal brother really likes to joke.

129
00:07:25,757 --> 00:07:26,757
Father, forgive me.

130
00:07:26,781 --> 00:07:27,982
I've had too much to drink

131
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,718
and said something inappropriate on a whim.

132
00:07:30,016 --> 00:07:31,217
Please punish me, Father.

133
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,487
Father,

134
00:07:35,054 --> 00:07:36,055
I'm innocent.

135
00:07:36,322 --> 00:07:37,923
I just want to stay by Father's side

136
00:07:37,924 --> 00:07:38,858
and help relieve his worries.

137
00:07:38,925 --> 00:07:40,068
I've never overstepped my bounds.

138
00:07:40,092 --> 00:07:41,492
I hope Father can see this clearly.

139
00:07:41,827 --> 00:07:42,595
Father,

140
00:07:42,596 --> 00:07:44,072
Since royal brother came to Jiangnan,

141
00:07:44,096 --> 00:07:45,507
he has been constantly thinking of Mother.

142
00:07:45,531 --> 00:07:46,232
He's been going to places

143
00:07:46,233 --> 00:07:47,600
where Mother used to go.

144
00:07:47,867 --> 00:07:49,567
How could he possibly form factions
and seek private gains

145
00:07:49,568 --> 00:07:50,579
as the royal elder brother said?

146
00:07:50,603 --> 00:07:52,003
Please investigate clearly, Father.

147
00:08:08,487 --> 00:08:11,757
This family banquet is boring.

148
00:08:12,792 --> 00:08:14,326
Let me help Your Majesty go back

149
00:08:14,327 --> 00:08:15,561
and have a good rest.

150
00:09:12,051 --> 00:09:14,053
Surround Yin Qi's courtyard.

151
00:09:14,077 --> 00:09:15,508
Wait for the prince's
order before taking action.

152
00:09:15,532 --> 00:09:16,532
Yes.

153
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:45,851
Fifth Prince Yin Qi,

154
00:09:46,238 --> 00:09:47,440
greedy for power,

155
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,636
conspired with Su He to rebel.

156
00:09:51,757 --> 00:09:53,125
Upon hearing this,

157
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,959
I dispatched troops to rescue the emperor
and protect Father's safety.

158
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,228
To protect Father's safety.

159
00:09:56,996 --> 00:09:59,031
Yin Qi resisted stubbornly.

160
00:09:59,412 --> 00:10:00,445
I had no choice but to

161
00:10:00,733 --> 00:10:01,813
shoot him dead on the spot.

162
00:10:02,034 --> 00:10:03,034
Understand?

163
00:10:03,622 --> 00:10:05,223
As for Pei Yanzhi...?

164
00:10:07,179 --> 00:10:09,048
I want to see with my own eyes

165
00:10:09,661 --> 00:10:12,297
his heartbroken expression
when he hears that Yin Qi is dead.

166
00:10:12,978 --> 00:10:16,215
That look of utter despair.

167
00:10:16,549 --> 00:10:17,549
Understood, Master.

168
00:10:51,063 --> 00:10:51,396
Prince,

169
00:10:51,437 --> 00:10:52,026
Are you alright?

170
00:10:52,051 --> 00:10:52,551
I'm fine.

171
00:10:52,552 --> 00:10:54,032
Let's go to Father's bedroom quickly.

172
00:10:59,925 --> 00:11:00,726
Help!

173
00:11:00,793 --> 00:11:01,761
There are assassins!

174
00:11:01,794 --> 00:11:02,995
Protect the emperor!

175
00:11:06,191 --> 00:11:07,559
Deshun, Deshun!

176
00:11:09,802 --> 00:11:10,603
What's going on?

177
00:11:10,669 --> 00:11:12,029
Why are they making such a racket?

178
00:11:12,738 --> 00:11:14,298
The imperial palace is heavily guarded.

179
00:11:14,406 --> 00:11:15,975
How could assassins get in?

180
00:11:24,950 --> 00:11:26,118
Who are you?

181
00:11:26,218 --> 00:11:27,696
How dare you break into
the imperial palace at night?

182
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,164
We're following the
orders of the fifth prince

183
00:11:29,188 --> 00:11:30,556
to come and take Yin Zhao's head.

184
00:11:33,726 --> 00:11:34,726
Qi'er,

185
00:11:35,494 --> 00:11:36,962
he's usually so well-behaved.

186
00:11:37,196 --> 00:11:38,631
How could he possibly commit such a

187
00:11:38,655 --> 00:11:39,855
treasonous and rebellious act?

188
00:11:51,577 --> 00:11:53,212
You are all subjects of Daxing.

189
00:11:53,612 --> 00:11:55,092
But you've been deceived by Yin Zhou.

190
00:11:55,714 --> 00:11:57,149
If you turn back now,

191
00:11:57,449 --> 00:11:58,851
I can spare your lives.

192
00:11:59,018 --> 00:11:59,819
Stop talking nonsense.

193
00:11:59,952 --> 00:12:01,921
Tonight is the night you
and the old emperor die.

194
00:12:01,987 --> 00:12:02,987
Kill!

195
00:12:37,289 --> 00:12:38,090
Something's not right.

196
00:12:38,091 --> 00:12:39,191
Go report to the master.

197
00:12:39,725 --> 00:12:40,725
Yes.

198
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:46,198
Go, hurry!

199
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:06,452
I don't want to just run away like this.

200
00:13:07,319 --> 00:13:08,120
Princess,

201
00:13:08,153 --> 00:13:09,855
do you know what you're saying?

202
00:13:10,188 --> 00:13:10,822
Of course.

203
00:13:11,056 --> 00:13:12,657
I'm the sixth princess.

204
00:13:12,791 --> 00:13:14,193
At such an important moment,

205
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,195
why can I only run away?

206
00:13:16,795 --> 00:13:18,364
If I can't help royal brother,

207
00:13:18,564 --> 00:13:20,132
and if something happens to him,

208
00:13:20,199 --> 00:13:22,234
how will I be able to
face others in the future?

209
00:13:22,768 --> 00:13:23,969
At a time of life and death,

210
00:13:24,003 --> 00:13:25,204
you're telling me this?

211
00:13:25,471 --> 00:13:27,039
I know you're trying to stop me,

212
00:13:27,206 --> 00:13:27,640
but I...

213
00:13:27,673 --> 00:13:28,207
I...

214
00:13:28,208 --> 00:13:29,375
Are you really sure?

215
00:13:30,576 --> 00:13:31,576
What?

216
00:13:32,044 --> 00:13:33,512
If you have this determination,

217
00:13:33,779 --> 00:13:35,748
then this lady will
accompany you to the end.

218
00:13:45,691 --> 00:13:49,962
Master, master, master!

219
00:13:50,429 --> 00:13:51,796
The guards in the emperor's bedroom

220
00:13:51,797 --> 00:13:52,965
were originally all killed.

221
00:13:53,198 --> 00:13:55,398
But two teams of guards
suddenly appeared from nowhere.

222
00:13:55,467 --> 00:13:57,907
And for some reason,
the archers didn't take their positions.

223
00:13:59,038 --> 00:14:00,139
If we fight head-on,

224
00:14:00,572 --> 00:14:02,132
we don't have a sure chance of winning.

225
00:14:02,474 --> 00:14:03,675
The brothers sent me to report

226
00:14:03,676 --> 00:14:04,810
and ask for your decision.

227
00:14:05,878 --> 00:14:07,012
How's Yin Qi?

228
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:08,959
There aren't many guards in his courtyard.

229
00:14:09,048 --> 00:14:10,849
We should be able to succeed quickly.

230
00:14:12,251 --> 00:14:13,695
No matter how many
guards are in the bedroom,

231
00:14:13,719 --> 00:14:15,154
they can't match our death squads.

232
00:14:16,959 --> 00:14:18,359
Let the death squads I arranged

233
00:14:18,383 --> 00:14:20,952
outside the imperial palace rush in.

234
00:14:21,727 --> 00:14:23,128
The most important task tonight

235
00:14:23,362 --> 00:14:25,965
is to kill Yin Qi and Father.

236
00:14:26,732 --> 00:14:27,732
Understood, Master.

237
00:14:33,272 --> 00:14:34,173
There are guards by Father's side

238
00:14:34,174 --> 00:14:35,975
that I didn't know about.

239
00:14:36,842 --> 00:14:37,842
Yin Qi,

240
00:14:37,997 --> 00:14:38,997
It's him.

241
00:14:39,859 --> 00:14:40,893
It must be him.

242
00:14:42,648 --> 00:14:44,450
Don't worry, Your Highness.

243
00:14:44,883 --> 00:14:46,050
Now, the emperor firmly believes

244
00:14:46,051 --> 00:14:47,753
that Yin Qi is planning a rebellion.

245
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,922
As long as Yin Qi is dead,

246
00:14:50,122 --> 00:14:51,590
there will be no evidence left.

247
00:14:52,157 --> 00:14:55,160
Then, Your Highness
will have all the power.

248
00:15:20,686 --> 00:15:22,187
Those thieves have all retreated.

249
00:15:24,690 --> 00:15:27,559
Are my reinforcements here?

250
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,560
Your Majesty,

251
00:15:28,694 --> 00:15:29,895
let's go quickly.

252
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:31,987
If the barbarians rush in later,

253
00:15:32,231 --> 00:15:34,600
we won't even have a chance to escape.

254
00:15:49,014 --> 00:15:49,548
You...

255
00:15:49,915 --> 00:15:50,915
You...

256
00:15:52,017 --> 00:15:53,017
You...

257
00:16:29,588 --> 00:16:30,923
From today on,

258
00:16:30,947 --> 00:16:33,449
I finally don't have to be
controlled by others anymore,

259
00:16:34,326 --> 00:16:35,727
and compromise for survival.

260
00:16:41,867 --> 00:16:43,335
Yin Qi, Yin Qi,

261
00:16:44,002 --> 00:16:47,172
you're the ultimate defeated opponent.

262
00:16:49,848 --> 00:16:50,991
Congratulations, Your Highness.

263
00:16:51,162 --> 00:16:52,364
Your wish

264
00:16:52,388 --> 00:16:53,388
has been fulfilled.

265
00:17:39,858 --> 00:17:40,858
This position

266
00:17:43,095 --> 00:17:44,095
finally

267
00:17:44,630 --> 00:17:46,031
belongs only to me.

268
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,172
Rebellious son!

269
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:02,481
Father!

270
00:18:03,121 --> 00:18:04,121
You...

271
00:18:04,416 --> 00:18:05,416
Royal brother,

272
00:18:05,951 --> 00:18:07,019
you've lost.

273
00:18:14,272 --> 00:18:15,864
It seems I've come
at the right time.

274
00:18:37,149 --> 00:18:38,149
Father!

275
00:18:39,318 --> 00:18:39,718
Father!

276
00:18:39,751 --> 00:18:40,752
Come with me quickly!

277
00:18:41,259 --> 00:18:42,260
Where are you taking me?

278
00:18:43,889 --> 00:18:44,889
Father,

279
00:18:47,793 --> 00:18:48,827
all of this

280
00:18:49,795 --> 00:18:51,395
was done by your royal elder brother,

281
00:18:51,396 --> 00:18:52,396
right?

282
00:18:52,731 --> 00:18:53,432
Father,

283
00:18:53,498 --> 00:18:54,700
You've guessed it.

284
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:56,435
This isn't the place to talk.

285
00:18:56,768 --> 00:18:58,170
Come with me to see someone.

286
00:18:58,303 --> 00:19:00,472
All truths will be revealed.

287
00:19:03,575 --> 00:19:05,577
Don't move, don't move.

288
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,480
Fengsun,

289
00:19:09,681 --> 00:19:11,601
You've conspired with
the Central Plains people,

290
00:19:11,883 --> 00:19:13,118
betrayed your kin.

291
00:19:13,619 --> 00:19:17,122
Aren't you afraid of divine punishment?

292
00:19:19,324 --> 00:19:20,959
Why are you asking me, Uncle?

293
00:19:22,094 --> 00:19:24,529
Uncle should know better than anyone

294
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:27,199
that I want to

295
00:19:28,367 --> 00:19:29,687
slice you into a thousand pieces.

296
00:19:30,188 --> 00:19:31,188
Fengsun,

297
00:19:31,436 --> 00:19:32,604
I've treated you well.

298
00:19:33,872 --> 00:19:39,211
I've even raised Aruna as if
she were my own daughter.

299
00:19:39,444 --> 00:19:40,711
And yet you betrayed me!

300
00:19:40,712 --> 00:19:41,712
Bullshit!

301
00:19:41,813 --> 00:19:43,415
You took advantage of Harchagai's death,

302
00:19:43,615 --> 00:19:44,615
kidnapped the princess,

303
00:19:44,683 --> 00:19:46,728
and forced the master to come to
the Central Plains as a hostage.

304
00:19:46,752 --> 00:19:48,896
With your long-standing
ambition for the Khan's throne,

305
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,122
if the gods have eyes,

306
00:19:50,188 --> 00:19:51,590
you'll be the first to be punished.

307
00:19:53,892 --> 00:19:55,427
I warned you, Uncle,

308
00:19:55,794 --> 00:19:58,555
not to get involved in the succession
struggle in the Central Plains.

309
00:19:58,730 --> 00:20:00,198
But you, Uncle,

310
00:20:01,099 --> 00:20:02,179
just wouldn't listen to me.

311
00:20:05,537 --> 00:20:06,537
Uncle,

312
00:20:07,072 --> 00:20:08,640
Reaching this point today,

313
00:20:09,274 --> 00:20:12,577
you can only blame yourself.

314
00:20:15,714 --> 00:20:16,714
Su He,

315
00:20:18,517 --> 00:20:19,517
You...

316
00:20:20,052 --> 00:20:21,052
Your Majesty,

317
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:22,454
For so many years,

318
00:20:22,921 --> 00:20:24,321
I've been sending messages to Su He

319
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,391
just to gain his trust.

320
00:20:29,394 --> 00:20:30,562
I just didn't expect that

321
00:20:31,002 --> 00:20:33,205
the Crown Prince would
exploit Su He's ambition

322
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:35,767
and try to ally with him

323
00:20:36,201 --> 00:20:38,570
to usurp the throne.

324
00:20:44,042 --> 00:20:45,042
Yin Zhao,

325
00:20:45,977 --> 00:20:48,113
You've won by luck this time,

326
00:20:49,114 --> 00:20:50,849
not because you're capable.

327
00:20:51,817 --> 00:20:53,552
It's because you're lucky.

328
00:20:53,952 --> 00:20:57,055
If you were born in the Talhan tribe,

329
00:20:57,355 --> 00:20:58,355
I'm afraid

330
00:20:58,857 --> 00:21:01,259
you wouldn't even qualify to fight me.

331
00:21:04,096 --> 00:21:05,330
The winner becomes king,

332
00:21:06,098 --> 00:21:07,178
the loser becomes a bandit.

333
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:09,260
Do whatever you want with me,

334
00:21:10,001 --> 00:21:11,169
I'm at your mercy.

335
00:21:13,438 --> 00:21:14,438
Father,

336
00:21:14,773 --> 00:21:17,376
I was able to find out in time

337
00:21:17,409 --> 00:21:19,690
that the royal brother was
conspiring with Su He to rebel

338
00:21:20,512 --> 00:21:22,748
all thanks to Yan Zhi's
enduring humiliation for years,

339
00:21:23,482 --> 00:21:24,582
making Su He think

340
00:21:24,583 --> 00:21:26,551
that Yan Zhi was his spy planted in Daxing.

341
00:21:26,852 --> 00:21:29,454
This is how their ambitions
and claws were revealed.

342
00:21:29,888 --> 00:21:31,123
This rebellious son!

343
00:21:31,656 --> 00:21:32,858
Where is he now?

344
00:21:33,191 --> 00:21:35,160
I won't spare him lightly!

345
00:21:36,528 --> 00:21:37,528
Speak!

346
00:21:37,929 --> 00:21:40,132
What's the signal you
agreed upon with Yin Zhou?

347
00:21:46,004 --> 00:21:47,606
You can kill me, but I won't say.

348
00:21:48,507 --> 00:21:49,507
Good.

349
00:21:49,841 --> 00:21:51,243
Then I'll grant you your wish.

350
00:22:11,029 --> 00:22:12,029
Stop!

351
00:22:19,237 --> 00:22:21,039
It seems Uncle has also learned

352
00:22:21,239 --> 00:22:24,042
that a wise man knows
when to submit in the Central Plains.

353
00:22:25,444 --> 00:22:26,444
Speak quickly!

354
00:22:29,648 --> 00:22:31,449
We had an agreement.

355
00:22:32,684 --> 00:22:34,019
After the deed is done,

356
00:22:34,352 --> 00:22:39,858
I'll order someone to
set off two smoke bombs.

357
00:22:53,471 --> 00:22:56,374
Haven't I treated you and
the queen well enough?

358
00:22:57,409 --> 00:22:59,109
You dare to conspire with outsiders

359
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:00,855
and attempt to kill
your father and brother,

360
00:23:00,879 --> 00:23:02,080
and usurp the throne?

361
00:23:03,315 --> 00:23:05,517
You're truly a rebellious son!

362
00:23:07,352 --> 00:23:09,254
I've spoiled you too much,

363
00:23:09,461 --> 00:23:11,362
making you arrogant and complacent.

364
00:23:11,656 --> 00:23:14,593
How dare you covet my throne!

365
00:23:15,961 --> 00:23:16,961
Father,

366
00:23:17,929 --> 00:23:20,131
You ask me why I rebelled?

367
00:23:21,099 --> 00:23:22,734
Don't you know?

368
00:23:23,401 --> 00:23:26,171
You're the one who started all this!

369
00:23:26,271 --> 00:23:27,072
Father,

370
00:23:27,272 --> 00:23:28,272
You...

371
00:23:28,874 --> 00:23:30,108
What nonsense are you talking?

372
00:23:31,476 --> 00:23:32,711
You've played political games,

373
00:23:33,278 --> 00:23:35,480
deliberately pitting my
brothers against each other.

374
00:23:35,714 --> 00:23:37,616
You watched us from on high,

375
00:23:37,649 --> 00:23:38,649
fighting and grabbing.

376
00:23:39,618 --> 00:23:42,721
Making me think I could
become the crown prince.

377
00:23:43,922 --> 00:23:44,922
In the end,

378
00:23:45,123 --> 00:23:47,359
I was just a pawn

379
00:23:47,492 --> 00:23:48,492
in your political games.

380
00:23:50,996 --> 00:23:51,996
How comfortably

381
00:23:52,731 --> 00:23:54,399
do you sit on this dragon throne?

382
00:23:54,633 --> 00:23:55,633
Nonsense!

383
00:23:56,968 --> 00:23:58,570
Who taught you to say this?

384
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:00,438
Was it the queen?

385
00:24:00,839 --> 00:24:01,573
Come here!

386
00:24:01,574 --> 00:24:03,241
Bring the queen here!

387
00:24:03,909 --> 00:24:05,810
I'll interrogate her in person.

388
00:24:06,678 --> 00:24:07,678
Mother!

389
00:24:08,179 --> 00:24:09,714
Mother knows nothing about this.

390
00:24:10,248 --> 00:24:12,284
Mother is just a woman in the palace.

391
00:24:12,857 --> 00:24:14,893
She sees all the concubines around you,

392
00:24:15,253 --> 00:24:17,255
and as the queen, she can't be jealous.

393
00:24:18,376 --> 00:24:19,409
She vents all her anger

394
00:24:19,557 --> 00:24:21,326
on me.

395
00:24:23,094 --> 00:24:24,329
Have you ever

396
00:24:25,230 --> 00:24:29,834
cared about me, your
son, even for a moment?

397
00:24:30,035 --> 00:24:31,136
How dare you!

398
00:24:31,803 --> 00:24:33,238
The glory of your maternal family

399
00:24:33,271 --> 00:24:34,739
was all given by me.

400
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:36,508
Even your ability to resist me

401
00:24:36,574 --> 00:24:38,109
was given by me.

402
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:40,979
What more do you want?

403
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,680
Royal brother,

404
00:24:42,881 --> 00:24:43,648
now that things have come to this,

405
00:24:43,649 --> 00:24:45,150
are you still obsessed?

406
00:24:45,650 --> 00:24:47,419
You keep saying

407
00:24:47,686 --> 00:24:49,988
that everything today was forced upon you,

408
00:24:50,655 --> 00:24:52,724
but the one who covets power

409
00:24:52,958 --> 00:24:54,159
is you.

410
00:24:54,926 --> 00:24:56,561
If it weren't for your greed for power,

411
00:24:57,395 --> 00:24:58,506
you wouldn't have failed today.

412
00:24:58,530 --> 00:24:59,531
What do you know?

413
00:25:03,234 --> 00:25:05,637
You've had your mother's
love since you were a child,

414
00:25:06,137 --> 00:25:07,772
and Father's favoritism.

415
00:25:08,907 --> 00:25:09,907
Even

416
00:25:11,109 --> 00:25:13,612
such a loyal dog.

417
00:25:16,348 --> 00:25:17,348
You...

418
00:25:18,883 --> 00:25:19,883
You...

419
00:25:21,086 --> 00:25:22,287
Do you know

420
00:25:23,054 --> 00:25:26,925
what I've been through these years?

421
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:29,460
Royal brother,

422
00:25:29,894 --> 00:25:31,029
Stop this.

423
00:25:31,763 --> 00:25:33,331
Father will spare your life.

424
00:25:34,299 --> 00:25:35,400
Yin Qi,

425
00:25:37,802 --> 00:25:39,971
I've failed today,

426
00:25:40,805 --> 00:25:43,008
I've been defeated by myself.

427
00:25:44,109 --> 00:25:45,977
You, born of a lowly woman,

428
00:25:46,411 --> 00:25:48,179
how dare you lecture me?

429
00:25:57,889 --> 00:25:58,889
Yin Qi,

430
00:25:59,124 --> 00:26:00,525
I did think about

431
00:26:01,126 --> 00:26:02,394
sparing your life.

432
00:26:02,827 --> 00:26:06,164
But you kept taking what
belonged to me over and over.

433
00:26:06,931 --> 00:26:10,068
Even the little bit of love
and trust from Father,

434
00:26:10,335 --> 00:26:11,436
you wanted to take away.

435
00:26:12,871 --> 00:26:13,871
Why?

436
00:26:14,839 --> 00:26:16,107
Why you all,

437
00:26:16,608 --> 00:26:18,710
why won't you all leave me alone?

438
00:26:23,515 --> 00:26:26,818
All of this started because of you.

439
00:26:27,852 --> 00:26:29,254
Since that's the case,

440
00:26:29,954 --> 00:26:31,356
even though I've failed,

441
00:26:32,557 --> 00:26:33,557
I,

442
00:26:33,725 --> 00:26:35,165
will make you accompany me in death.

443
00:26:56,815 --> 00:26:57,815
Why?

444
00:26:58,216 --> 00:26:59,684
Why did you stop me?

445
00:27:05,457 --> 00:27:09,961
If Your Highness admits
your mistake to the emperor,

446
00:27:12,997 --> 00:27:15,200
His Majesty will surely spare your life.

447
00:27:16,868 --> 00:27:17,869
But

448
00:27:20,238 --> 00:27:23,041
if you kill Yin Qi,

449
00:27:25,110 --> 00:27:26,110
you'll really

450
00:27:28,713 --> 00:27:30,715
have no way back.

451
00:27:37,589 --> 00:27:38,589
No!

452
00:27:38,990 --> 00:27:39,990
Don't go!

453
00:27:40,258 --> 00:27:41,392
Don't leave me!

454
00:27:42,193 --> 00:27:43,193
Please!

455
00:27:44,329 --> 00:27:46,431
If even you leave me,

456
00:27:47,232 --> 00:27:48,833
I'll really have nothing left.

457
00:27:51,523 --> 00:27:52,523
Your Highness,

458
00:27:54,438 --> 00:27:55,438
don't cry.

459
00:27:58,896 --> 00:27:59,896
Your Highness

460
00:28:00,912 --> 00:28:02,413
is the best person

461
00:28:07,218 --> 00:28:08,686
in this world.

462
00:28:09,788 --> 00:28:10,788
Live well,

463
00:28:12,891 --> 00:28:13,892
live on.

464
00:28:17,328 --> 00:28:20,331
If there's an afterlife...

465
00:28:26,771 --> 00:28:28,173
I still want to be

466
00:28:29,207 --> 00:28:30,207
the prince's

467
00:28:33,778 --> 00:28:35,280
sharp blade.

468
00:29:33,671 --> 00:29:34,472
Zhou'er.

469
00:29:34,572 --> 00:29:35,572
You.

470
00:30:08,006 --> 00:30:09,841
Only now do I understand

471
00:30:11,075 --> 00:30:12,877
that long ago,

472
00:30:13,811 --> 00:30:15,647
the idealistic

473
00:30:16,748 --> 00:30:18,549
and ambitious Yin Zhou

474
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:25,456
was already killed

475
00:30:26,724 --> 00:30:28,326
by my father and mother.

476
00:30:31,095 --> 00:30:32,095
Today,

477
00:30:33,698 --> 00:30:36,401
the only person in the world

478
00:30:36,968 --> 00:30:38,770
who truly loved me

479
00:30:44,809 --> 00:30:46,010
has also left me.

480
00:31:24,048 --> 00:31:25,850
You think you've won?

481
00:31:28,753 --> 00:31:29,753
No,

482
00:31:29,854 --> 00:31:31,389
there are never any winners.

483
00:31:35,159 --> 00:31:36,160
You,

484
00:31:37,528 --> 00:31:39,130
will end up like me,

485
00:31:42,166 --> 00:31:44,969
living forever in an endless hell,

486
00:31:46,738 --> 00:31:49,173
watching helplessly as

487
00:31:49,207 --> 00:31:50,908
you lose everything.

488
00:31:55,279 --> 00:31:56,681
Today,

489
00:32:00,218 --> 00:32:01,218
it is I

490
00:32:04,522 --> 00:32:05,522
who am freed.

491
00:32:08,893 --> 00:32:09,893
Zhou'er.

492
00:32:28,679 --> 00:32:29,679
Zhou'er.

493
00:32:30,348 --> 00:32:31,348
Zhou'er.

494
00:32:32,950 --> 00:32:33,950
Father.

495
00:32:34,285 --> 00:32:35,285
Father.

496
00:32:35,486 --> 00:32:36,486
Father Emperor!

497
00:32:52,370 --> 00:32:53,370
Zhou'er.

498
00:33:03,341 --> 00:33:04,008
Yan Zhi.

499
00:33:04,116 --> 00:33:05,316
We've really done it.

500
00:33:05,349 --> 00:33:06,117
This time around,

501
00:33:06,118 --> 00:33:07,318
we're both still alive.

502
00:33:08,779 --> 00:33:09,779
A Qi,

503
00:33:10,388 --> 00:33:11,656
it was you who did it.

504
00:33:13,191 --> 00:33:14,859
You changed our fates,

505
00:33:15,593 --> 00:33:16,593
and even

506
00:33:17,195 --> 00:33:18,429
the fate of the Daxing Empire.

507
00:33:24,202 --> 00:33:25,202
But.

508
00:33:26,938 --> 00:33:28,739
I can't bring myself to be happy.

509
00:33:29,974 --> 00:33:32,243
Seeing what happened to the
Crown Prince and Wei Ziming,

510
00:33:33,277 --> 00:33:34,979
I don't feel like I've won.

511
00:33:36,114 --> 00:33:37,548
The Crown Prince was right.

512
00:33:38,349 --> 00:33:39,917
In this treacherous imperial city,

513
00:33:40,418 --> 00:33:41,752
there are never any winners.

514
00:33:44,388 --> 00:33:45,388
A Qi,

515
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:46,791
don't think like that.

516
00:33:47,692 --> 00:33:49,594
If Yin Zhou had really
ascended to the throne,

517
00:33:50,194 --> 00:33:51,474
and gained control of the world,

518
00:33:52,430 --> 00:33:53,764
what kind of life

519
00:33:54,832 --> 00:33:56,367
would the people of Daxing have had?

520
00:34:00,137 --> 00:34:01,172
You're right.

521
00:34:02,306 --> 00:34:03,407
In my previous life,

522
00:34:04,375 --> 00:34:05,843
I spent three years at the border,

523
00:34:06,043 --> 00:34:07,763
seeing too much suffering among the people.

524
00:34:08,212 --> 00:34:09,814
It really opened my eyes.

525
00:34:15,353 --> 00:34:16,521
What are you doing here?

526
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:17,401
Brother,

527
00:34:17,474 --> 00:34:18,642
the carriage is ready.

528
00:34:22,827 --> 00:34:23,961
You two,

529
00:34:24,328 --> 00:34:25,029
is there something

530
00:34:25,029 --> 00:34:26,029
I don't know about?

531
00:34:28,099 --> 00:34:28,900
Good sister,

532
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:29,900
let's go, let's go.

533
00:34:40,011 --> 00:34:41,011
Tang'er,

534
00:34:41,512 --> 00:34:43,614
On the day we parted ways,

535
00:34:44,882 --> 00:34:48,252
I always felt we would meet again.

536
00:34:50,788 --> 00:34:51,789
I never expected that

537
00:34:52,557 --> 00:34:53,858
after all these years,

538
00:34:55,393 --> 00:34:56,393
we would truly

539
00:34:57,161 --> 00:34:59,363
never meet again in this life.

540
00:35:01,085 --> 00:35:01,885
Aunt,

541
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:03,534
don't be too sad.

542
00:35:03,935 --> 00:35:05,603
I'm sure Aunt Tang missed you terribly

543
00:35:05,803 --> 00:35:07,738
while she was alive.

544
00:35:08,072 --> 00:35:09,750
Even though you haven't
seen each other for years,

545
00:35:09,774 --> 00:35:11,375
your hearts have always been connected.

546
00:35:11,809 --> 00:35:13,777
That's better than being together every day

547
00:35:13,778 --> 00:35:15,513
yet lacking any understanding.

548
00:35:17,281 --> 00:35:18,883
Sister Xianyue is absolutely right.

549
00:35:20,051 --> 00:35:21,752
Mother would think the same way.

550
00:35:37,668 --> 00:35:38,668
Aunt Lin,

551
00:35:39,003 --> 00:35:40,538
after we return to the capital,

552
00:35:41,939 --> 00:35:42,939
I'll have to trouble you

553
00:35:43,441 --> 00:35:44,976
to take care of Mother.

554
00:35:46,477 --> 00:35:47,712
Of course.

555
00:35:48,512 --> 00:35:49,512
By the way,

556
00:35:50,014 --> 00:35:51,415
when are you leaving?

557
00:35:52,516 --> 00:35:53,918
We're leaving tomorrow.

558
00:35:54,285 --> 00:35:55,720
After the Crown Prince passed away,

559
00:35:56,053 --> 00:35:58,213
Father Emperor seems to
have aged ten years overnight.

560
00:35:59,523 --> 00:36:01,243
It's better to return to the capital early.

561
00:36:01,859 --> 00:36:03,327
You'll face many more challenges

562
00:36:03,794 --> 00:36:06,030
when you return to the capital,

563
00:36:08,399 --> 00:36:09,634
but I believe

564
00:36:11,435 --> 00:36:12,603
that no matter what,

565
00:36:13,337 --> 00:36:15,172
as long as you stand together,

566
00:36:15,573 --> 00:36:17,375
you'll overcome any obstacle.

567
00:36:19,176 --> 00:36:21,979
This matter is definitely
related to Talhan.

568
00:36:22,413 --> 00:36:23,714
As a hostage,

569
00:36:25,683 --> 00:36:27,284
I must give Daxing an explanation.

570
00:36:28,119 --> 00:36:28,753
Yan Zhi,

571
00:36:28,819 --> 00:36:30,187
you're being too formal.

572
00:36:30,588 --> 00:36:31,188
Don't worry,

573
00:36:31,255 --> 00:36:32,975
I'll plead with King Father on your behalf.

574
00:36:36,794 --> 00:36:37,794
Xianyue,

575
00:36:38,796 --> 00:36:40,231
let's go back.

576
00:36:56,447 --> 00:36:57,014
This one,

577
00:36:57,014 --> 00:36:57,615
This one,

578
00:36:57,648 --> 00:36:58,816
not this one.

579
00:36:58,916 --> 00:37:00,318
Wrap up all the rest for me.

580
00:37:01,886 --> 00:37:02,886
My lucky star,

581
00:37:02,953 --> 00:37:04,188
you have excellent taste!

582
00:37:05,289 --> 00:37:06,489
You don't need to buy so much.

583
00:37:06,791 --> 00:37:07,992
The capital has everything.

584
00:37:08,326 --> 00:37:10,761
Besides, I'm a princess.

585
00:37:11,449 --> 00:37:13,251
These are all specialties from Jiangnan.

586
00:37:13,831 --> 00:37:14,831
Besides,

587
00:37:14,999 --> 00:37:16,533
what your father buys for you

588
00:37:16,534 --> 00:37:17,701
and what I buy for you

589
00:37:17,702 --> 00:37:18,702
are not the same.

590
00:37:21,572 --> 00:37:22,707
Here you go.

591
00:37:23,474 --> 00:37:25,309
Let's go to the rouge shop up ahead.

592
00:37:26,210 --> 00:37:27,377
You're practically
shouting from the rooftops

593
00:37:27,378 --> 00:37:28,978
that you're the richest man in Jiangnan.

594
00:37:29,113 --> 00:37:30,353
You don't have to be so polite.

595
00:37:31,916 --> 00:37:32,616
Buying rouge?

596
00:37:32,717 --> 00:37:33,717
Top-quality rouge.

597
00:37:35,119 --> 00:37:36,759
You won't miss me when I leave, will you?

598
00:37:38,723 --> 00:37:40,124
Don't flatter yourself.

599
00:37:40,191 --> 00:37:41,191
I was thinking that since

600
00:37:41,192 --> 00:37:42,512
you can't often leave the palace,

601
00:37:42,593 --> 00:37:44,204
I should buy you
plenty to last you a while.

602
00:37:44,228 --> 00:37:45,948
In case you secretly cry yourself to sleep.

603
00:37:52,269 --> 00:37:53,637
Selling rouge!

604
00:37:55,806 --> 00:37:56,806
Aunt Lin,

605
00:37:57,308 --> 00:37:58,442
we'll take our leave now.

606
00:37:59,210 --> 00:38:00,778
We'll reunite after

607
00:38:01,045 --> 00:38:02,085
you return to the capital.

608
00:38:04,115 --> 00:38:05,116
Good children,

609
00:38:05,883 --> 00:38:07,151
take care on your journey.

610
00:38:07,685 --> 00:38:10,676
I've already arranged
for people to escort you.

611
00:38:38,649 --> 00:38:39,450
Heshu,

612
00:38:39,517 --> 00:38:40,718
we should go.

613
00:39:00,237 --> 00:39:01,237
Aunt Lin,

614
00:39:01,472 --> 00:39:02,472
I'll take my leave.

615
00:39:38,576 --> 00:39:39,576
Yanzhi,

616
00:39:40,044 --> 00:39:41,512
Are you really going back to Talhan?

617
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:43,880
After all these years,

618
00:39:45,216 --> 00:39:46,150
Su He has turned Talhan

619
00:39:46,151 --> 00:39:47,318
into a mess.

620
00:39:47,852 --> 00:39:48,852
I think

621
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,554
it's even worse than what

622
00:39:50,588 --> 00:39:52,188
you saw on the border in your past life.

623
00:39:53,390 --> 00:39:54,792
I must go back to Talhan

624
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,220
to help my elder brother revive it

625
00:39:57,761 --> 00:39:58,761
and let my people

626
00:39:59,530 --> 00:40:01,131
live a peaceful and prosperous life.

627
00:40:06,570 --> 00:40:07,972
I understand what you're saying,

628
00:40:09,073 --> 00:40:10,975
I just can't bear to part with you.

629
00:40:12,276 --> 00:40:14,278
Why don't I go back with you?

630
00:40:14,411 --> 00:40:16,547
I'm very familiar with Talhan.

631
00:40:16,714 --> 00:40:18,516
The lamb in Talhan is the best.

632
00:40:27,291 --> 00:40:28,291
You...

633
00:40:28,592 --> 00:40:29,692
But now, as the only

634
00:40:29,693 --> 00:40:31,195
adult prince of the Daxing Dynasty,

635
00:40:31,695 --> 00:40:33,163
you have heavy responsibilities.

636
00:40:33,564 --> 00:40:34,564
Don't talk nonsense.

637
00:40:35,599 --> 00:40:37,201
I understand what you're saying.

638
00:40:38,536 --> 00:40:40,538
But with your abilities,

639
00:40:40,671 --> 00:40:41,839
in no more than three years,

640
00:40:42,039 --> 00:40:43,406
Talhan will surely become

641
00:40:43,407 --> 00:40:44,775
what you envision it to be.

642
00:40:48,913 --> 00:40:50,814
If you need anything,

643
00:40:50,915 --> 00:40:52,650
I will do my utmost.

644
00:40:58,689 --> 00:40:59,689
What's wrong?

645
00:41:00,991 --> 00:41:03,761
Maybe I caught a cold.

646
00:41:04,094 --> 00:41:05,214
The journey has been tiring.

647
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,200
Fifth Prince,

648
00:41:10,267 --> 00:41:11,267
Young Master,

649
00:41:12,836 --> 00:41:15,639
His Majesty wants you to go to
the imperial study for a discussion.

650
00:41:22,813 --> 00:41:23,813
Qi'er,

651
00:41:24,014 --> 00:41:26,534
You've rendered meritorious service
in protecting me this time.

652
00:41:26,817 --> 00:41:28,118
What reward do you want?

653
00:41:28,152 --> 00:41:29,219
Just tell me.

654
00:41:29,587 --> 00:41:31,655
I will surely grant it to you.

655
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:34,725
This is just my duty.

656
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:37,260
I dare not take credit for it.

657
00:41:43,934 --> 00:41:45,645
You can put righteousness above family ties

658
00:41:45,669 --> 00:41:47,538
and know what's important.

659
00:41:47,738 --> 00:41:50,908
It seems that Concubine
Chen’s teachings have paid off.

660
00:41:51,442 --> 00:41:52,242
Go ahead,

661
00:41:52,309 --> 00:41:53,577
what reward do you want?

662
00:41:55,212 --> 00:41:56,212
Your Majesty,

663
00:41:56,447 --> 00:41:58,649
I've been in Daxing for ten years now.

664
00:41:59,083 --> 00:42:00,083
During these ten years,

665
00:42:00,250 --> 00:42:01,684
I've been constantly

666
00:42:01,685 --> 00:42:03,205
missing the grasslands of my hometown.

667
00:42:03,654 --> 00:42:05,454
I earnestly request Your
Majesty's permission

668
00:42:05,522 --> 00:42:06,857
to let me return to Talhan.

669
00:42:07,324 --> 00:42:08,859
After I return to Talhan,

670
00:42:09,126 --> 00:42:10,527
I will surely govern the tribe well

671
00:42:10,761 --> 00:42:12,081
and obey Your Majesty's commands,

672
00:42:12,596 --> 00:42:14,156
never again letting border disturbances

673
00:42:14,298 --> 00:42:15,738
become a problem for both countries.

674
00:42:40,991 --> 00:42:41,991
Aunt,

675
00:42:42,059 --> 00:42:43,961
I'll finish going through
these accounts soon.

676
00:42:52,536 --> 00:42:54,138
The little boss is so diligent.

677
00:42:54,271 --> 00:42:55,711
It seems she doesn't miss me at all.

678
00:42:55,973 --> 00:42:57,174
Why are you back?

679
00:43:03,447 --> 00:43:05,416
My elder brother said we did a good deed

680
00:43:05,549 --> 00:43:06,517
by protecting His Majesty.

681
00:43:06,518 --> 00:43:07,958
He went to plead with Father Emperor

682
00:43:08,018 --> 00:43:09,420
to allow me to stay in Jiangnan.

683
00:43:10,721 --> 00:43:12,456
We did a good deed?

684
00:43:23,667 --> 00:43:24,935
Let's go.
